text: Pionersky () is a rural locality (a selo) in Spartaksky Selsoviet, Yermekeyevsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 220 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 14 km from Yermekeyevo, 3 km from Spartak. == References == Category:Rural localities in Yermekeyevsky District
title: Pionersky, Yermekeyevsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
